Package Bags

Class LinkedBag<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • Bags.LinkedBag<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BagInterface<T>
    public class LinkedBag<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements BagInterface<T>
    Linked Bag implementation. Creates a linked bag that contains set operations of intersection, union, and difference. Interacting with this object uses the bag interface.
